---

POST /oauth/token HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8000
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id=my_foo&grant_type=password&scope=read+write&username=foo&password=pass

---

GET /oauth/authorize?client_id=my_foo&amp;response_type=token&amp;scope=read write&amp;redirect_uri=http://localhost:8000/hello/world HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8000
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

